kg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Finternational%2Fpele-on-lionel-messi-neymar-news-latest-deigo-maradona-kylian-mbappe-a8670141.html&d=BK1g1eN8jI%2B4p8cgbZaFdI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5b2f5213\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/pele-on-lionel-messi-neymar-news-latest-deigo-maradona-kylian-mbappe-a8670141.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb45acc06afb12cd83d123762f06da2644f36ca6","tid":930642,"uid":14719,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"收到風呢篇真嘢黎 連英國報導都有出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&ldquo;The 78-year-old Brazil icon has sensationally criticised Messi for being one-footed.<br />\n<br />\nHe also says the five-time Ballon d'Or winner's inability to head the ball means he was a better player.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"381913b1a1173f336bbf3409ca43724052966489","tid":930642,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6525a73490fc46601cf70102aaab5b823ec7b137","tid":930642,"uid":64809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"呢篇野真假混雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e987ecf2919b9e591fb0795d868d2a1b61f2e0","tid":930642,"uid":10757,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"尼馬回憶上月與老大哥的對話：「記得上個月跟他在酒吧聊天，談起球會來季目標，我預告自己今年將會大爆發，為球會重奪聯賽和歐聯。」<br />\n<br />\n「老大哥沒有回應，望著酒杯問我：『你知道英文字母的順序嗎？』我說當然知道，然後他就說：『N永遠排在M後面，這是定律，即使你成功，亦是在我的允許之下。』」<br />\n<br />\n「瞬間我明白了他意思了，他要永遠當球會的老大哥。於是我不忿地回應了一句：『那麼C排在M的前面又代表甚麼呢？』他馬上就黑面了，自此我們就沒有再說過話。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0505f2c43ac8aeeedd597